Sentencas: Layered perovskite oxides have ordered A-cations localizing oxygen vacancies, and may potentially improve oxygen ion diffusivity and surface exchange coefficient.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The A-site-ordered layered perovskite PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+delta (PBSC) was evaluated as new cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The material was characterized using electrochemical impedance spectroscopy in a symmetrical cell system (PBSC/Ce0.9Sm0.1O1.9 (SDC)/PBSC), exhibiting excellent performance in the intermediate temperature range of 500-700 degrees C. An area-specific-resistance (ASR) of 0.23 Omega cm(2) was achieved at 650 degrees C for cathode polarization.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The low activation energy (Ea) 124 kJ mol(-1) is comparable to that of La0.8Sr0.2Co3-delta.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A laboratory-scaled SDC-based tri-layer cell of Ni-SDC/SDC/PBSC was tested in intermediate temperature conditions of 550 to 700 degrees C. A maximum power density of 1045 mW cm(-2) was achieved at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interfacial polarization resistance is as low as 0.285, 0.145, 0.09 and 0.05 Omega cm(2) at 550, 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Layered perovskite PBSC shows promising performance as cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+δ layered peroyskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
